{"tid":1519193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日唔係最後一戰啊！！！","createTime":"2019-08-30T13:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:54:21.000Z","uid":204486,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"28d1ffa85d99940b0f59fec05767354469f07c51","tid":1519193,"uid":204486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"我都好想聽日佢哋搞緊急法或者出老解<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我覺得佢哋唔搞嘅機會好大<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日佢哋一定會封鐵，set rb拉人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日只要人一多，佢哋就難清場<br />\n<br />\n再一次好似之前咁癱瘓港島就可以<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話邊得啊，邊會有咁多人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以快啲做文宣，推post啦仆街</span><br />\n<br />\n另外加上 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋係香港人啊仆街</span><br />\n<br />\n呢三月證明咗，幾無可能嘅我哋都做到<br />\n<br />\n由6.9至今幾多次覺得無可能<br />\n但我哋都做到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋聽日真係要小心，盡量唔好被捕啊<br />\n<br />\n畜龍衝出嚟，真係要試下<strong>打狗救人</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果聽日少咗好多手足<br />\n<br />\n對唔對得住呂麗搖巴架飛機啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明白大家好緊張，有心理準備係好事<br />\n但聽日好大機會唔係End game<br />\n盡量不被捕，9.1機場見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果好攰好想放棄<br />\n<br />\n請你記住我哋煲底除口罩之約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fca4c762dbb5c17de9d0288ec383d5ea10fa47","tid":1519193,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2